^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The theoretical reason for playing 1430 is very unimportant for all but the world class players. I like 0314 because it is just more logical. The clubs shows 0, diamonds shows 1, hearts shows 2. Just like old fashioned Blackwood. |
