NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The reason for 1430 is the Q ask when hearts are trumps. It turns out that 1430 is a more common response than 0314 (but not by much). So if playing hearts, you can't ask for the trump Q over 5D but you can over 5C (by bidding 5D). That is why 1430 is just slightly better. but for most players, it is way more confusing, and I favor simplicity whenever possible.|
